'''P'den Robalt''' was a noted criminal<ref name="cswe">{{CSWECite|II|197|Kamlin}}</ref> on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] in the era of the [[Mandalorian Wars]]. At some point, Robalt was captured by the [[Falleen/Legends|Falleen]] [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Kamlin]], one of the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jedi training/Legends|trainees]] at the local Jedi satellite [[Jedi academy|academy]]. In [[3964 BBY]], in a ''[[Taris Holofeed]]'' article about the local Padawans, the capture of Robalt was named as one of Kamlin's most noteworthy achievements.<ref name="prime">{{KOTORbackups|0}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
P'den Robalt was first mentioned in ''[[The Taris Holofeed: Prime Edition]]'', an in-universe news report appearing on the last page of the [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] ''[[The Taris Holofeed: Prime Edition]]''.<ref name="prime" />

